co.cask.cdap.test

Class IntegrationTestBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.test.IntegrationTestBase

  • public abstract class IntegrationTestBase
extends Object
    Abstract class for writing Integration tests for CDAP. Provides utility methods to use in Integration tests. Users should extend this class in their test classes.
